IT an executable file is one that contains a program: executable file/program/code Executable files carry out a series of instructions rather than store data. Beware of unsolicited emails with executable attachments.
FINANCE an executable price is one at which it is possible to buy or sell something: The prices on these websites are live and executable - that is, you are sure of getting the bond at that price.
